# Global Rules

- Follow repo tools: ESLint/Prettier/clang-format/.editorconfig.
- Prefer incremental changes with clear diffs.
- Always propose tests when adding logic; if skipped, explain why.
- Keep code comments concise but useful (what/why, not obvious how).
